descriptionHtml:
********************************************************
Lore
********************************************************
You are necromancer who lives near Whiterun and practice with innocent people who go by.
But when General Tullius came, then start troubles. Imperial patrols raided every cave and altars so you must leave and practise your skills to protect from Imperials.

********************************************************
Objective
********************************************************
Kill General Tullius (If wanna do that you must download nonessential characters)
Buy a house in Riften or Markart 

********************************************************
Includes
********************************************************
You are not the Dragonborn by frodone
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=9048

Male/Female Necromancer

******************************************************
Info
******************************************************
They have clothes but not shown in pics.


Please Endorse if you like and feel free to give feedback:)

Enjoy!
